  "title": "Cloud Engineer (Kubernetes experience)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Plan, execute, monitor, and control all technical aspects of projects.</li><li>Lead or contribute to new system/network infrastructure setups or upgrades.</li><li>Support operational systems in line with contractual Service Level Agreements (SLAs).</li><li>Conduct routine preventive maintenance and manage operational activities efficiently.</li><li>Prepare comprehensive project documentation and reports.</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues promptly.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong knowledge of Windows Server OS and Linux OS; experience in virtualized environments is a plus.</li><li>Hands-on experience with virtualization, hypervisors, and the Nutanix platform is an advantage.</li><li>Understanding of VPNs and firewall appliances is beneficial.</li><li>Familiarity with network switches and routers is preferred.</li><li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills to articulate technical concepts to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</li><li>Proactive, dynamic, and analytical with strong conceptual thinking abilities.</li><li>Able to work independently and collaboratively, with strong interpersonal skills.</li></ul><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>bianca@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.</p><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312).</p>",
